quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  28,85,"Pellet, jippin…óo Alqur'aana on O farli yottingol nde ngol e maa…óa, gollitira ko woni e mayre, ko ruttoowo ma udditugol Makka. An Nulaa…óo, maakan sirkoo…ìe …ìen: Ko Joomi am …ìuri anndude ardu…óo e peewal, e won…óo e majjere …ìanngunde."
  28,86,"An Nulaa…óo, a wonaano ado nulal ngal, tam∆¥ininoo …óo jippineede wahayu Alqur'aana on e maa…óa. Si wanaa tun ko e yurmeende Alla he…ìir…óaa …óum. Wata a wonu walloowo heefer…ìe …ìen e majjere ma…ì…ìe."
  28,87,"Wata …ìee sirkoo…ìe falo ma ko sa…óti woo, gaay e Aajeeje Alla …óen, …ìaawo jippineede e maa…óa, haa selaa fii janngugol …óe yottina. Noddu yim…ìe …ìen, faade e gom…óingol Alla, wootin…óina Mo, gollira sari'a Makko on. Wata a wonu jeyaa…óo e sirkanoo…ìe Alla …ìen; wonu bajjin…óinoowo Mo, rewa Mo Kanko tun."
  28,88,"Wata a rewdu e Alla, rewetee…óo goo. Rewetee…óo e goonga alaa, ko woori Mo. Huunde kala ko re'ay…óum, si wanaa Jaati Makko Kin. Ko Kanko tun, √±aawuugol ko O muuyi woodani; ko ka Makko kadi woni ruttorde mon, √ëalnde Darngal, fii hesbeede yo…ìee."
  29,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim: yewtere sugu …óee Aayeeje yawtiino ka fu…ó…óorde cortewol (simoore)Al-Baqarah."
  29,2,"E yim…ìe …ìen sikku, fii …ìe wi'ii: Men gom…óinii Alla, …ìe accirte non, hara …ìe jarribaaka, haa gom…óinal ma…ì…ìe ngal …ìannga tigiri? Wanaa no …ìe sikkiri non."
  29,3,"Gom…óii, Men jarribike …ìen adinoo…ìe …ìe. Maa Alla fe√±√±inir …ìannginangol on, goongu…ìe …ìen, e gom…óinal ma…ì…ìe nagl, e fende fenu…ìe …ìen e …óum."
  29,4,"Kaa ko ronndorii…ìe bone sirku ekn mun kon sikku, wonnde …ìe laawoto Men, haa …ìe da…óa lepte Amen? Fii √±aawoore ma…ì…ìe nden bonii; tawde …ìe laawotaako Alla, …ìe da…óataa kadi lepte Makko …óen, si …ìe maayii e keeferaaku."
  29,5,"Kala jortii…óo hawroygol e Alla √ëalnde Darngal, fii yo O warjo mo, yo o anndu pellet, caatal(lajal) ngal Alla happi ngal fii …óum, ko hewtawl jooni. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo haalaaji jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Anndu…óo kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe. Huunde laawotaako Mo e …óum, O yo…ìitoyay …ìe fow e mun."
  29,6,"Kala tii…ónii…óo e dewal, o wo…ó…óitii e geddi, o wonii fii Alla, haray ko hoore-makko o tii…ónanii; tawde nafa …óum on, ko e makko artata. Alla kan, ko yondinii- …óo e tageefo ngon fow; dewal ma…ì…ìe …ìeydataa Mo, goopi ma…ì…ìe kadi …óuytataa Mo."